Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-cz] <roomba> PTYX why are there so many wallet companies? Guarda, pungo, agama, magnum. You guys are all part of komodo in some way, is this some type of divide and concur strat?

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-cz] <PTYX> @rainbro7 each service has their own wallet with its own purpose. Guarda and Magnum are third party wallet providers. We created Chameleon because we wanted to offer our clients an easy to use wallet with more functionality than coinomi.

Author: Gateway#3763
Content: [dscrd-cz] <PTYX> Pungo has a whole ecosystem of products including a debit card, exchange, and escrow system. So they created a version of Agama to suite their needs. It might seem like the wallets are competing with one another but they complement the ecosystem.
